%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Setup
%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  * [Ruby] 1.8.6 or newer.

  * [RubyGems] 1.3.6 or newer.

Installing:

    gem install detest

Upgrading:

    gem update detest

Removing:

    gem uninstall detest
